snippet.title: Grapple Dogs: Cosmic Canines - Official Announcement Trailer | gamescom 2023
snippet.description:
Check out the announcement trailer for Grapple Dogs: Cosmic Canines, the sequel to the 2D pixel-art platformer, Grapple Dog. Swing, bounce, and wall run through this cute platforming game from Medallion Games. Grapple Dogs: Cosmic Canines is coming in 2024.

#IGN #gamescom #Gaming
